<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/94/432">Pub. L. 94–432</ref> effective <date date="1977-01-01">Jan. 1, 1977</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/94/432/s405/b">section 405(b) of Pub. L. 94–432</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s1521">section 1521 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idc2a8a4e2-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1975 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/94/169/tII/s202">Pub. L. 94–169, title II, § 202</ref>, <date date="1975-12-23">Dec. 23, 1975</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/89/1021">89 Stat. 1021</ref>, as amended by <ref href="/us/pl/94/432/s101">section 101 of Pub. L. 94–432</ref>, eff. <date date="1976-09-30">Sept. 30, 1976</date>, provided that the amendment made by that section is effective <date date="1976-01-01">Jan. 1, 1976</date>.</p>
</note>
