</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idc2a8a4e4-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1971 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/92/197">Pub. L. 92–197</ref> effective <date date="1972-01-01">Jan. 1, 1972</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/92/197/s10">section 10 of Pub. L. 92–197</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s1311">section 1311 of this title</ref>.</p>
