<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idc2a8a4e5-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1970 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/91/588">Pub. L. 91–588</ref> effective <date date="1971-01-01">Jan. 1, 1971</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/91/588/s10/a">section 10(a) of Pub. L. 91–588</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s1521">section 1521 of this title</ref>.</p>
